text: Scooby-Doo! The Mystery Begins is a franchise. It's on Cartoon Network. The franchise must be about a bunch of characters: 4 humans - Fred, Velma, Daphne, and Shaggy - and a brown dog named Scooby-Doo. The fun never ends. == Voice Cast == *Robbie Amell as Fred *Kate Melton as Daphne *Hayley Kiyoko as Velma *Nick Palatas as Shaggy *Frank Welker as Scooby-Doo Category:Scooby-Doo movies Category:Warner Bros. direct-to-video movies
title: Scooby-Doo! The Mystery Begins
